{"tid":620853,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人真事] 琴日搭地鐵 見到藤原拓海同佢老母真人","createTime":"2018-04-07T19:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T09:58:55.000Z","uid":48304,"like":11,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"03c67ca5c128bd64e69f7e845b0369d8d40b1210","tid":620853,"uid":48304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T19:49:31.000Z","msg":"岩岩上到車 心諗真黑仔 岩岩好得我無位坐<br />\n唯有行埋塊玻璃度挨下 順便偷聽下隔黎講野<br />\n<br />\n仔：媽 我睇野越黎越慢呀<br />\n<br />\n我即刻轉頭望過去 佢同佢老母各自碌緊電話<br />\n全程都無乜眼神接觸<br />\n<br />\n媽：又黎？上年又係咁，洗唔洗帶你睇醫生呀<br />\n<br />\n我好奇繼續觀察 睇真啲 原來佢用緊android 係部電話越用越慢<br />\n心諗唔怪得之 我即刻走埋去介紹佢用iPhone<br />\n佢地聽完半信半疑 但經我熱烈推介之下 直接係深水埗落車 過左宏基出機<br />\n頭先去七仔撞番佢地 仲話部iphone用左兩年都仲好快 好多謝我咁話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2486a4d33f16bbe9c468dcc2e7fae22844a8d6","tid":620853,"uid":158977,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T20:11:07.000Z","msg":"岩你老母 岩石"},{"pid":"5d012b672fc67224e847930b19b036df3d47f05f","tid":620853,"uid":33694,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T20:12:19.000Z","msg":"on99"},{"pid":"2adb7fe343d6c34bbde40be55a5f92db6024441d","tid":620853,"uid":22553,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T20:20:26.000Z","msg":"又岩岩上車又用咗兩年，二手機比人用咗兩年呀?"},{"pid":"63641b3efeddd66579189b3c4dc9d94141fa7db5","tid":620853,"uid":76527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T20:32:36.000Z","msg":"都唔知你up 乜鳩"},{"pid":"01c50fdd76de8e4d0657f8aab9f057a3f32f7684","tid":620853,"uid":48304,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:39:47.000Z","msg":"an狗不願面對 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc02cf0ca32d48d8c484ac54b50b039bbe7de0d7","tid":620853,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0af0896f32e5a7e0f4f6524031de8cb